Date: 0/0/1869
Source: Punch or the Auckland Charivari
Author:
Vol / Page: 171
Edition:
Quote: Angels Whispers: the bugle sound for `Grog oh!'- that  mysterious operation of serving out measures of grog  into double its former quantity - it already having undergone sundry chemical changes.
