Date: 0/0/1925
Source: Soldier and Sailor Words
Author: FRASER & GIBBONS
Vol / Page: 7
Edition:
Quote: ANGEL'S WHISPER: An old Service phrase, originally, for the Defaulters' bugle-call and also for the Reveille or `Rouse'; the awakening bugle-call in the morning.
